Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we rolling?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.21,0:00:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not like I care...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.71,0:00:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need for you to film any of this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, today...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take divine retribution on those four
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.39,0:00:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about the "4 idiots" of Gaki no Tsukai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.13,0:00:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all helpless
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been angry{ {\alphaHFF\t(3000,495,\alpha100)} at them for so long
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.17,0:01:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been making me angry for so many years!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they'll all face
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.51,0:01:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My divine retribution
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.54,0:01:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(666,0)\an4\fnVerdana\fscx63\shad0\bord4\blur4\pos(402,249.334)}TRANSLATION: SHION\NTYPESET & QC: KEDOMAS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.54,0:01:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(666,0)\an6\fnVerdana\fscx63\shad0\bord4\blur4\pos(1398,777.333)}SHIONNOTSUKAI.WORDPRESS.COM
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.73,0:01:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The one I can't forgive the most\N between the four of them is Hamada, that idiot
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.86,0:01:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The things he did to me to this very day...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.66,0:01:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember them all?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to 20 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.94,0:01:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Tanaka! Let's all gather!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.17,0:01:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is from a show we did over 20 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.64,0:01:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,An episode called "It's Tanaka! Let's all gather!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,500)}Just take a look at how guilty that idiot is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,For this bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They had to snap at my poor host skills
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.69,0:01:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So that the whole episode's atmosphere would be ruined
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.86,0:01:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the prank was all about
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The small fry won!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.89,0:01:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs100\fade(0,400)\c&H421FD8&\3c&H4BD4FF&\4c&HFF855A&\pos(892,756)}Small fry won!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the champion?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.49,0:01:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.33,0:01:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we actually broadcast this on TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You think we should not?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:02:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really the best you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being foul-mouthed, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that how you call that shit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You see how he actually hit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.45,0:02:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's watch that one more time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.02,0:02:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that how you call that shit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry, we're sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That one actually hit me too
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.23,0:02:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He grabbed my head
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He grabbed my head so tightly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We were joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.64,0:02:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That was no joke
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,None of that was a joke
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He clearly hit me with that racket
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This was supposed to be a prank
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So you gotta arrange it accordingly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But regardless,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada, that idiot,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit me so hard with that goddamn racket!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And pulled my hair like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.79,0:02:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitting someone's head for a laugh is typical of Osaka's comedy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But to keep that style and bring it to Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.23,0:03:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he relies so much on violence
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so quick at being violent, 'cause he thinks it's fun
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.74,0:03:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And he can't just stop
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just a remnant of Osaka, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not all there is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In "Hot Blooded! Hamada's Cram"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot-Blooded!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada's Cram School!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a series with more episodes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's this section, the "non-stop club"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In which we have to keep on moving until he tells us to stop
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We basically have to keep on moving
