Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.79,0:05:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet the flour is the only flavor he knows
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't think he knows the flavor of comedy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a flour-dish remnant, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That Hamada, here in Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But this isn't the end of it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,As you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also the "Hamada's aging trial"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to start the second "Hamada's Aging Trial"
