Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the second time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,As more and more years go by, \NHamada gets more and more senile
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This episode wanted to prove this theory
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not just this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,As you know, he cares a lot about Inomoto and the Dorians
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have some evidence from his manager
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(722,903.334)}This one really shocked me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He asks "what's my schedule for tomorrow?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He exchanged messages with his manager
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"For now, you have tomorrow off"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\i1\pos(475.5,1005.333)}"toriaezu"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,950)}- That's his manager
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, Hamada replied...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:05:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And he called his manager
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:06:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,With a very threatening tone in his voice
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.06,0:06:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It should have been fine
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hey! What do ya mean?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dorians have a day off? No one ever told me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He misread "for now" as "Dorians"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(708,1006)\i1}"toriaezu"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This really shocked me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(722,894)}How can you misread "for now" as "Dorians"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\i1\pos(796,838)}"toriaezu"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This really shows how he's aging
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And the way he snapped, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's starting to look like Eiji Bando
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Mr. Bando?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just an angry old dude
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how he's becoming\N- Bando gets angry in the same way
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not something worth a laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It just doesn't feel right
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada himself believes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That if we make an episode out of this, we can laugh it away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, "isn't it ok if we can just laugh at it?" -- He's getting it wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The same goes for our audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They think it's good as long as they can laugh at him
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all delusional!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This show itself is misleading us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just promoting Hamada's senility!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a remnant of senility!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.74,0:07:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Hamada is
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The same can be said to Hamada's partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.38,0:07:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's nice to himself, but severe with others
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Check this out
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.09,0:07:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In this episode
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We entered this stage to perform a play
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And we had to fall over
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,When the timing required us to do so
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to fall over, but only once
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's the best comedic fall we can do
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna learn a lot from this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see his legs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He's wearing knee pads
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The four of us had to fall over countless times
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And we didn't wear any knee pads
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto only fell down one time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But he asked the staff to wear knee pads
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a remnant of knee pads, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto always says that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.65,0:08:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"Comedy has to be objective to work", but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We recently had this episode, the "Breathless Club"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(734,267.333)\fad(400,1000)\shad0\bord5.5\blur0.6\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\b1\i1}Lactic Acid Frenzy!\N Battle - Read "The Turtle and the Hare"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.49,0:08:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"Lactic Acid Franzy! Battle - \N Read 'The Turtle and the Hare'!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto will face the challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(736,160.667)}It's a challenge about how much\N one can read after producing lots of lactic acid
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(942,667.333)}You can hold it!{\c&H60ECF9&} I'm starting to feel nervous
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, it's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, stop, stop
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(930,627.333)}I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(930,627.333)}I can't run for that long!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the tape for a sec
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He could run for only 26 seconds, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see, before doing this bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He said "I usually run a lot, I won't produce any lactic acid!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"It won't tire me at all!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"If I'm doing it, it's not going to be fun at all"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what he said to the staff
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But what's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't run at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He could only run for 26 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's "objective" about you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But this isn't the only shocking footage
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more right after it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,From this point on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There were less than 10 seconds left
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the machine
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta be kidding me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Can this actually happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.87,0:09:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,763.333)}The staff was so worried {\c&H60ECF9&}they plugged the whole thing off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:09:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:09:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726,691.333)}- See this? Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, what {\i1}is{\i0} this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't run at all
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But because he was still trying
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.39,0:10:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The staff got worried about him
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And they decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,To plug the machine off
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.33,0:10:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't even done it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was, like, two years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto made a post on Twitter
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4\fade(500,0)\pos(348,718.667)}"I'm worried about my juniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,0)\pos(636,819.333)}Matsumoto will move on."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I'm really worried about him
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you move?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you move, move, run?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hosei
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He started from Osaka
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And being a "remnant of Osaka", he moved to Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he became a remnant of Tokyo and went back to Osaka
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always dragging along old stuff with him
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.64,0:10:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So what can I say about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He became some sort of flawless embodiment of remnants
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.61,0:11:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Every year, on the opening for our New Year Ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes! New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes! New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes! New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes! Yes! New Year!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes! New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes! New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.61,0:11:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes! New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes! Yes! New Year!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If they ask me, "what's a remnant of Osaka?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd reply "It's this"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"This is what a remnant of Osaka looks like"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's repeating the same thing for years
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we have Endo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he---
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have much to say about him
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he's got nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not even a "remnant"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just like a bell
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A bell without a ball inside
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, a bell which makes no sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But this Endo here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.19,0:12:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Has once found something which "made a sound"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogo! Ogo! Ogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.47,0:12:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This really made a sound
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(718,894)}Louder!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs35\an4\bord0\pos(266,78.666)}If you missed this episode, \Nyou can find it subbed on {\c&H7BBEF6&}shionnotsukai.wordpress.com:\N {\c&H00EAFF&}Life Of The “Ogoo” Endo Pteranodon
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is one of the things which made more sound for him
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But regardless of it, this guy completely forgot about "Ogoo"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And didn't do it at all after that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He just threw it away
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And never tried to use it again, not even once
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with his "Ogoo"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He could have conquered the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I've talked a lot about them
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The one pulling the strings of those idiots
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Hamada
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Check this out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no idea what's going on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because it's not ethical to broadcast this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why all you see is a censored clip
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.14,0:13:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've {\3c&H0C0D9B&\4c&H0C0D9B&}[censored]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Until it was destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I bet all I just said got censored too, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no way of knowing what's going on here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:13:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.76,0:14:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I'm going to punish them all
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To my heart's content
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Without holding back
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,First time ever on Gaki no Tsukai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a 100-hit Badminton combo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And win 1 million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord0\pos(703,900)}Tsukitei Hosei\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hMatsumoto Hitoshi\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hHamada Masatoshi\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hEndo Shozo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,1 million each?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No way\N - Oh, it's shared
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,500)}As you can see, Tanaka is absent today
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(716,910)\fad(0,350)}- Ah, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, it's finally revenge time
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They think I didn't show up because I'm sick,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.63,0:14:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I'll reach them and I'll get my revenge
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright guys, let's aim at that sweet million!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's do this
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta make it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.61,0:14:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice one, like this
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on...\N- I think it went too far
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't hit it with the edge, that's not how it works
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!\N - Sorry about that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki could have gone for it, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But he didn't go at all\N - It was Endo's
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start again
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,16\N- We're doing great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,17...\N - We can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,19!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,28!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That damned spot...\N- I thought it was Endo's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You both hesitated
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.82,0:15:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should call it\N - I agree
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, "I'm going!" or such\N - Alright, let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Two...\N- Nice one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try again
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:15:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's call it when it's ours
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I didn't go for it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think we can do this\N - We should try it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should aim lower?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Endo's quite good at it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just go\N - Yep
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you please...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Lower it a bit, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go\N - Not much progress, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.38,0:16:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because the distance is off--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going!\N - Feel free to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You all ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,One
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this, kinda
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh boy...\N - Get ready
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We can definitely do this
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not take any break\N - Ok
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Three...\N - Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It went right through it, man
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.13,0:17:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yama-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yama-chan, what the?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a grip, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be helped
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It can happen, I know
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go...\N - One!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.54,0:17:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shozo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, we can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.01,0:17:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No way\N - We're losing focus   - You're right
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.38,0:17:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a 100 combo is too much for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How about, like, 51?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree, we should aim at that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,One!\N- If we can pull this off...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Here
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too high
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.86,0:18:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Go get it, Hamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.77,0:18:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting a single ball...\N- I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?\N - I can't figure out the right distance
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hitting it too softly\N - But I just got that one, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! One...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap!\N - I'm sorry about that...{Hamada is probably whispering "honma... honma..." (come on... for real...)}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.85,0:18:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it goes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get it back, come on
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go\N - One!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start again
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.65,0:19:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not even reaching me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.26,0:19:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it flying over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.56,0:19:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Counting on you!\N - Alright, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.23,0:19:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada, whenever you want!\N - Oh, I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada, please
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:19:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? We can barely even hit it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, man
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.45,0:20:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Yama-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, we don't have much time
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We barely even made any progress\N - That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yama-chan what's wrong? Did it slip?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, it just fell
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,One!\N - Nice
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Two-- hey, can you even see it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can, sorry\N - Come on, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best here
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see it, but...\N - Matsumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you\N - It's there
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right there\N- Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't even pick it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.85,0:20:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's yours, Hamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Five!\N- Go get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.65,0:20:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Five!\N - Go get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your turn, Hamada
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.68,0:21:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on\N - Go, Hamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go for that million!\N - We're almost there
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.49,0:21:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go already
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling tired?\N - We are, actually
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't even reach five
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even five?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's at least go for five\N - That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.43,0:21:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's enough for them to realize\N they should never do any of that again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My revenge was successful
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We had fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a bit hard to see?\N - Yeah, I agree
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.79,0:21:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree, I can't see that well myself
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what makes it fun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.88,0:21:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,One... two...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.64,0:21:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.07,0:22:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,staff) Ok, we're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.04,0:22:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.87,0:22:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka, that fucking hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.39,0:22:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When you slammed it on my face, it hurt so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.31,0:22:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.58,0:22:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've felt Tanaka's kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.18,0:22:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In the sweetness of this cream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs50\pos(722,718)\shad0\bord8\blur4\3c&H9F3120&}BEFORE THE RECORDING
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.48,0:22:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\fs50\pos(722,718)\shad0\bord3\3c&H9F3120&}BEFORE THE RECORDING
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.73,0:22:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning\N- Morning
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.86,0:22:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This script...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.56,0:22:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Badmouths Osaka and Kansai so much, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts my heart, I swear
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.90,0:22:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I actually pull this off?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.58,0:22:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.78,0:22:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.78,0:22:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just an old dude empty laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.05,0:22:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's director is Ishikawa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.21,0:22:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(706,902)}- Ishikawa, huh
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.25,0:22:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his debut
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.35,0:22:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,0)}If I don't perform well on this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.99,0:22:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to hate me so much after this
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.47,0:23:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we even reach five?\N - Not even five
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.57,0:23:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The first throw was so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.84,0:23:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for all of this
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.97,0:23:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.34,0:23:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it went just fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.28,0:23:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,For a moment I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.22,0:23:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This was going to be a reverse-prank\N and Hamada would hurt me again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.66,0:23:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart was racing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.73,0:23:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't breathe easily
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that the original plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.78,0:23:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the plan was...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,For you to act and choose when to end it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.13,0:23:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so I could have done more?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.79,0:23:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... that's not what I heard before
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad it worked out, now I see
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.04,0:23:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.60,0:23:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.92,0:23:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, thank you so much!
